# Navigation
<ctrl>-[    -> back
<ctrl>-]    -> forward
<ctrl>-o    -> open file
<F5>        -> reload
<ctrl>-<F5> -> reload and override cache
<esc>       -> stop


# Current Page
<space>         -> go down a screen
<shift>-<space> -> go up a space
<end>           -> go to the bottom of the page
<home>          -> go to the top of the page
<ctrl>-+ / --   -> zoom in/out
<ctrl>-0        -> reset zoom to 100%


# Search
/                -> quick find
<ctrl>-f         -> find
<ctrl>-g         -> find again (=next)
<ctrl>-<shift>-g -> find previous
<esc>            -> close (quick) find bar


# Windows and Tabs
<ctrl>-w                  -> close tab
<ctrl>-<shift>-w          -> close window
<ctrl>-<shift>-<pagegup>  -> move current tab left
<ctrl>-<shift>-<pagedown> -> move current tab right
<ctrl>-<home>             -> move current tab to the start
<ctrl>-<end>              -> move current tab to the end
<ctrl>-t                  -> new tab
<ctrl>-n                  -> new window
<ctrl>-<shift>-p          -> new private window
<ctrl>-<tab>              -> go to next tab
<ctrl>-<shift>-<tab>      -> go to previous tab
<alt>-<enter>             -> open address in location bar n new tab
<ctrl>-<shift>-t          -> undo closing tab
<ctrl>-<shift>-n          -> undo closing window
<alt>-1                   -> go to tab 1 (also works with 2-8)
<alt>-9                   -> go to last tab


# Bookmarks and Stuff
<ctrl>-d         -> bookmark current page
<ctrl>-b         -> toggle bookmarks sidebar
<ctrl>-<shift>-o -> open bookmark window
<ctrl>-<shift>-y -> show downloads tab
<ctrl>-<shift>-a -> show addons tab

# Developer Tools
<ctrl>-<shift>-i -> toggle developer tools
<shift>-<F2>     -> toggle developer toolbar
<ctrl>-<shift>-m -> toggle reponsive design view
<shift>-<F4>     -> show scratch pad
<ctrl>-u         -> show page source tab
<ctrl>-i         -> show page info


# Miscellaneous
<del>          -> delete selected autocomplete entry
<F11>          -> toggle full screen mode
<alt>          -> toggle menu bar
<ctrl>-<alt>-r -> toggle reader mode
<ctrl>-l       -> select location bar, version 1
<alt>-d        -> select location bar, version 2
<ctrl>-j       -> select location bar, version 3
<ctrl>-m       -> mute/unmute audio

